(2246, 370, 1, 'Preheat oven to 325 degrees.'),
(2247, 367, 2, 'Combine the flour, baking powder, baking soda and salt; gradually add to creamed mixture and mix well. Stir in the German sweet chocolate, coconut and pecans.'),
