(2827, 452, 6, 'Add the cream and lemonjuice, season and keep warm.When the chicken is cooked, arrangeon a platter. Stir the coriander throughthe sauce and spoon into a bowl. Roughlychop the remaining walnuts and scatterover the chicken. Toast the pittas, cutinto wedges and serve alongside'),
(2828, 458, 7, 'Place the cookies on the baking sheet about 2 inches apart.'),
