(2830, 451, 7, 'Serve the avocado slices and tomato wedges on the side or mixed into the salad.'),
(2831, 460, 5, 'Transfer to a rack to cool completely, about 1 hour.'),
(2832, 458, 8, 'Bake for 11 to 12 minutes.'),
(2833, 461, 6, 'Mix into shortening mixture until just blended. Stir in chocolate chips and nuts.'),
(2834, 461, 7, 'DROP by rounded measuring tablespoonfuls 3 inches apart onto ungreased baking sheet.'),
(2835, 461, 8, 'BAKE 8 to 10 minutes for chewy cookies, or 11 to 13 minutes for crisp cookies. Cool 2 minutes on baking sheet on a cooling rack.'),
(2836, 461, 9, 'Remove cookies to rack to cool completely.'),
