(4785, 811, 1, 'Allow turkey to set at room temperature 30 minutes prior to roasting.Preheat the oven to 450F.In a bowl, mix to combine butter, orange zest, chopped sage, garlic, salt, and pepper. With your hands, separate the skin from the meat and rub half of the compound butter in between the skin and the meat. Evenly rub the remaining butter over the skin of the turkey. Truss the turkey or tie the legs together with cooking twine.'),
