(4819, 808, 4, 'Cut into small dice, then set aside.'),
(4820, 808, 5, 'Add the pasta to the boiling water and cook for 2 mins less than it says on the pack. Meanwhile, heat the oil in a large frying pan (you’ll need to use one with a lid) and add the garlic, sizzle for 2 mins until just starting to turn golden, then push to one side of the pan. Increase the heat and add the prawns and scallops, fry for 1-2 mins until the prawns are pink and the scallops are just turning golden, then scoop out of the pan and set aside on a plate.'),
(4821, 815, 10, 'Spread cream evenly over bottom layer of cake. Top carefully with top half of cake. Sprinkle lightly with confectioners’ sugar and serve immediately or refrigerate.'),
